{"type":null,"faqId":32739,"title":"摄像头为什么只有2000W像素，而不是2100W像素？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-family:Times New Roman;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀</span><span class=\"s1\">7</span><span>主摄像头使用了索尼</span><span class=\"s1\">IMX230</span><span>传感器，该传感器最大有效像素为</span><span class=\"s1\">2100W</span><span>。但出于均衡考虑，为了实现更好的拍照效果，荣耀</span><span class=\"s1\">7</span><span>摄像头只采用了其中的</span><span class=\"s1\">2000W</span><span>像素，这种设计在单反相机上也经常采用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7441","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748390000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":39,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"摄像头,像素","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}